title: Better Homes and Gardens: Knitting For Babies and Kids
description: If you love babies and children, you will love this collection of adorable sweaters, breezy summer tops, jazzy jumpers, delightful shorts, cozy hats, fun coats, baby toys, child's bathrobe and slippers, jackets, animal backpack, comfy mittens, kids' afghans, colorful rompers, interesting vests, baby blankets and cuddly animals. You will find 99 wonderful designs to knit for all your favorite babies and children.
